org.apache.spark.network.client

Class TransportResponseHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.spark.network.server.MessageHandler<ResponseMessage>
      • org.apache.spark.network.client.TransportResponseHandler

  • public class TransportResponseHandler
extends MessageHandler<ResponseMessage>
    Handler that processes server responses, in response to requests issued from a [[TransportClient]]. It works by tracking the list of outstanding requests (and their callbacks). Concurrency: thread safe and can be called from multiple threads.
